high_descs: Turn left and walk to the left side of the desk, with the trash bin on the floor.
Pick up the pencil from the trash bin.
Place the pencil on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Place a pencil on a desk.

high_descs: Turn around and then face to your right twice so that you are facing the side of the trash can
Pick up a pencil out of the trash can
Look up from the trash can
Put the pencil down on the desk
anns.task_desc: Take a pencil out of the trash and put it on the desk

high_descs: Walk over to the small black bin next to the wooden desk on your left.
Pick up the pencil out of the small black bin.
Look up at the wooden desk in front of you.
Put the pencil on the wooden desk.
anns.task_desc: Move a pencil from a small black bin to a wooden desk.
